        <p>
          
  Modus is the first major UPVC window and door system to offer the reassurance of a 12-year guarantee. And that comes without compromise on performance as Modus is A-rated for sustainability featuring 50% post-consumer recycled UPVC as standard. This enables us to offer better thermal performance than rivals. Combined with high security locked-in 6-chamber frame design Modus offers strength and resilience and style in abundance.

